My former band was called “Schrödinger’s Cat” because, similar to how the cat in the box was simultaneously alive and dead, we existed in a state of simultaneously having a name and not having a name.

Then the cops opened the box and found our bassist dealing meth on the side. Now we only exist in a state of not existing. Fuck you James.
